      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior appointments, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire an example of unparalleled integrity. Every aspect of this vehicle has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the most exacting requirements for quality and performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
