    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' experience without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
