      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it's finally time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, always kept it garage-stored, and there isn't a single scratch to be found. If you're looking for total perfection and that new-car feel, you just found it! I'd love for you to come take a look. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
