      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine showroom condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is absolute; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the double-VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, utilizing the factory M-variable differential lock and a perfectly balanced 50/50 weight distribution. Finished in original Carbon Black Metallic over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is uniform across all panels with no evidence of thermal cycling or road rash. This is a turn-key collector piece for the purist seeking the zenith of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
